Package: shksprwrdl
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of the 'wordle' game with Shakespeare's words
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ruben", "Hernandez", , "ruben@rubenhm.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment= c(ORCID="0000-0001-6474-9510"))
    )
URL: https://github.com/rubenhm/shksprwrdl
Description: This is a clone of the 'wordle' game
    https://www.powerlanguage.co.uk/wordle/  in R.
    It uses words from Shakespeare's plays, except for the most common words.
    The game allows for words with apostrophes.
